thread.title: Lesley Lang

author: Lesley Lang
title: Lesley Lang
text:
I highly recommend Danielle and the Servcorp team at Westpac House Adelaide for their professionalism and helpful nature.
I appreciate the global nature of the Servcorp enterprise and my ability to use its offices interstate and overseas, which are located in prime positions with excellent fit-outs and facilities.
Servcorp is a much valued asset for my business.
Lesley Lang
